<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Karanis</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Καλπουρνίωι Κονκέσσωι τῶι κρατίστωι ἐπιστρατήγωι 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Γεμέλλου τοῦ καὶ Ὡρίωνος Γαίου Ἀπολιναρίου Ἀντινοέως. 

    <lb n="3"/>οὗ ἐπέδωκα τῷ λαμπροτάτω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐπάρχωι</unclear> Αἰμιλίῳ Σατουρνίνῳ 

    <lb n="4"/>βιβλιδίου <handShift new="m2"/> καὶ <handShift new="m3"/> ἧς ἔτυχον αὐτοῦ <hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>ερᾶς ὑπογραφῆς ἀντιγραφον ὑπέταξα. ἀξιῶ, ἐάν σου 

    <lb n="5"/>τῇ τύχῃ <subst><add place="inline">δόξῃ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">δοξε</del></subst>, γράψαι τῷ διακειμένῳ ἐν τῷ Ἀρσινοείτῃ ἑκατοντάρχῃ πέμψαι 

    <lb n="6"/>τὸν <choice><corr>ἀντίδικον</corr><sic>αντιδιχον</sic></choice> ἐπὶ τὴν σὴν διάγνωσιν καὶ ἀκ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οῦ</unclear>σαί μου πρὸς αὐτὸν ὅπως <subst><add place="inline">τύχω</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">χυχω</del></subst> 

    <lb n="7"/>τῶν δικαίων. ἔστι δέ· 

    <lb n="8"/>Κυ<hi rend="diaeresis">ί</hi>ντωι <choice><corr>Αἰμιλίωι</corr><sic>αμιλλιωι</sic></choice> Σατουρνίνωι ἐπάρχωι Αἰγύπτου 

    <lb n="9"/>παρὰ Γεμέλλου τοῦ καὶ Ὡρίωνος Γα<hi rend="diaeresis">ί</hi>ου Ἀπολιναρίου Ἀντινοέως καὶ ὡς χρη-

    <lb n="10"/>ματίζω. ἐντυγχάνω, κύριε, κα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ὰ Κάστορος χειριστοῦ κώμης Καρανίδος τῆς 

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>Ἡρακ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">λ</supplied>είδου</corr><sic>ηρακειδου</sic></choice> μερίδος τοῦ Ἀρσινοείτου νομοῦ. <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὅ</unclear>δ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear> καταφρονήσας μου ὡς <choice><corr>ἐπισινοῦς</corr><sic>επισουνους</sic></choice>, 

    <lb n="12"/>μονόφθαλμος γὰρ ὢν τῷ δοκοῦντι ὁρᾶν οὐ βλέπω ὡς ἐν <choice><corr>ἀμφοτέροις</corr><sic>ανφοτεροις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="13"/>πονηρὸν εἶναι <choice><corr>ἄντικρυς</corr><sic>αντικροις</sic></choice>, ἠργολ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ά</supplied>βησέν με <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">καὶ</unclear> πρότερον ἐμὲ <choice><corr>ἐξυβρίσας</corr><sic>εξυβρεισας</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="14"/>δημοσίᾳ καὶ τὴν <choice><corr>μητέρα</corr><sic>μητεραν</sic></choice> μου, μετὰ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὸ</unclear> <choice><corr>πλείσταις</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πλισ</unclear>ταις</sic></choice> αὐτὴν πληγαῖς αἰκίσασθαι 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ πέλυκι ὅλας μου <choice><corr>τέσσαρας</corr><sic>τεσσαρες</sic></choice> θύρας <choice><corr>κατασχίσαι</corr><sic>κατασχεισαι</sic></choice> ὥστε ὅλην ἡμῶν τὴν 

    <lb n="16"/>οἰκίαν <choice><corr>ἀν<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">απ</supplied>επταμένην</corr><sic>ανεπταμενην</sic></choice> γενέσθαι καὶ <choice><corr>εὐεπίβατον</corr><sic>ευεπειβατον</sic></choice> παντὶ κακού<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ργῳ, τούτων</supplied> 

    <lb n="17"/><choice><corr>κατεσχισμένων</corr><sic>κατασχεισμενων</sic></choice> καὶ κατενηνεγμένων ἡμῶν μηδὲν <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὀφειλόντων</supplied> 

    <lb n="18"/>τῷ ταμείῳ, ὅθεν οὐδὲ σύμβολον <choice><corr>παραγαγεῖν</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">παραξαι</unclear></sic></choice> ἐτόλμησε <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μὴ ἀδικεῖν δι᾽</supplied> 

    <lb n="19"/>αὐτοῦ ἐλέγχηται ἢ ἐργολαβηκέναι. διὸ, σω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τῆρος</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>άξαντος τοὺς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀδικουμένους</supplied> 

    <lb n="20"/><choice><corr>σοι</corr><sic>συ</sic></choice> <choice><corr>προσιέναι</corr><sic>προσειεναι</sic></choice> ἀδεῶς τῶν δικαίων τευξομένους, ἀξιῶ ὑ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πὸ σοῦ, κύριε,</supplied> 

    <lb n="21"/>ἀκουσθῆναι καὶ <subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>ἐκδικηθῆναι</corr><sic>εγδικηθηναι</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">εκδικηθηναι</del></subst> <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>ν᾽ ὦ εὐεργε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τη</unclear>μένος, τὸν δὲ ἀ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ντίδικον πεμ</supplied>-

    <lb n="22"/>φθῆναι ἐξ αὐθεντίας σου ἐπὶ τὴν σὴν διάγνωσιν. Γέμελλος <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐπιδέδωκα</supplied>. 

    <lb n="23"/>Γερμανὸς ἔγραψα ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="6">ϛ</num> Μεσορ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὴ</unclear> <num value="18">ιη</num> τῷ κρατί<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">στῳ ἐπιστρα</supplied>-

    <lb n="24"/>τήγῳ ἔντυχε πρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὸ</unclear>ς τὰ αὐτοῦ μέρη οὐκ ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear>δεήσοντι· ἀπ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">όδος</supplied>. 

    <lb n="25"/><handShift new="m4"/> Γέμελλος ὁ καὶ <choice><corr>Ὡρίων</corr><sic>ωριωνος</sic></choice> ἐπιδέδωκα ὡς <choice><corr>πρόκειται</corr><sic>προκιται</sic></choice>. <gap extent="10" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="26"/>Πανεβτίχιος ἔγραψα ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ μὴ εἰδότος γράμματα. 

    <lb n="27"/><handShift new="m5"/> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="6">ϛ</num> Μεσορὴ ἐπαγομέν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ω</supplied>ν <num value="3">γ</num>. 

    <lb n="28"/>ἐπὶ τῶν τόπων ν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῦν</unclear> γενομένῳ 

    <lb n="29"/>ἔντυχε.  <handShift new="m6"/>  ἀπόδος. </ab></div><div n="meta.12263" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.12263" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="198" notBefore="198" type="textDate" value="0198-08-26">26. Aug. 198</date></p></div><div n="meta.12263" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 8-24: <date type="mentioned" value="0198-08-11">11. Aug. 198</date></p></div><div n="meta.12263" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">425</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">12263</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">425</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;6;425" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.12263" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">214</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.12263" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.12263" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" full="yes" type="ancientFindspot">Karanis</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" full="yes" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName cert="high" full="